# Icon Rules

- Use `@lucide/astro` for static UI icons in Astro components.
- Icons in header, sidebar, footer, cards, breadcrumbs, FAQs, and static sections must be rendered by Astro, not React.
- Use local inline SVG files only for brand/protocol logos such as Solana, Pump.fun, Raydium, Meteora, Orca, and LaunchLab.
- Do not use icon fonts.
- Do not use `react-icons`.
- Do not use animated icon libraries.
- Do not import icon libraries globally.
- Do not put icons behind client-side JavaScript when they can be rendered as static SVG.
- Keep icon size consistent:
  - Sidebar icons: `16px`
  - Card icons: `20px`
  - Hero/tool icons: `24px` or `32px` max
- Use `currentColor` so icons inherit text color from Tailwind classes.
- Decorative icons must include `aria-hidden="true"`.
- Meaningful icon-only buttons must include accessible labels.
